      "span_text": "Echocardiography of TG Mice LV mass and LV end-diastolic dimension (LVEDD) were determined as described earlier using echocardiography (ECHO) in age-and gender-matched (littermate) WT and TGs.  Briefly, LV mass was calculated from LV wall thickness and dimension measurements using an established formula."
